{"parse":{"title":"Armed violence reduction","pageid":30991666,"revid":787924357,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The concept of <b>armed violence reduction (AVR)</b> has gained significant in importance after the <a href=\"/wiki/Geneva_Declaration_on_Armed_Violence_and_Development\" title=\"Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development\">2006 Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development</a>. According to <a href=\"/wiki/OECD\" title=\"OECD\">OECD</a>, more than 740,000 people die each year as a result of the violence associated with <a href=\"/wiki/Armed_conflict\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Armed conflict\">armed conflicts</a> and large- and small-scale <a href=\"/wiki/Criminality\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Criminality\">criminality</a>. Furthermore, armed violence impedes humanitarian and socio-economic development and, hence, it is an obstruction to achieving the <a href=\"/wiki/Millennium_Development_Goals\" title=\"Millennium Development Goals\">Millennium Development Goals (MDG)</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Key_numbers_on_armed_violence_from_the_Geneva_Declaration_on_Armed_Violence_and_Development\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Key numbers on armed violence from the Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Key_numbers_on_armed_violence_from_the_Geneva_Declaration_on_Armed_Violence_and_Development\">Key numbers on armed violence from the Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Armed_violence_reduction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Key numbers on armed violence from the Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>More than 740,000 people have died directly or indirectly from armed violence - both conflict and <a href=\"/wiki/Violent_crime\" title=\"Violent crime\">criminal violence</a> - every year in recent years.</li>\n<li>More than 540,000 of these deaths are violent, with the vast majority occurring in non-conflict settings.</li>\n<li>At least 200,000 people - and perhaps many thousands more - have died each year in conflict zones from non-violent causes (such as <a href=\"/wiki/Malnutrition\" title=\"Malnutrition\">malnutrition</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Dysentery\" title=\"Dysentery\">dysentery</a>, or other easily preventable diseases) that resulted from the effects of war on populations.</li>\n<li>Between 2004 and 2007, at least 208,300 violent deaths were recorded in armed conflicts - an average of 52,000 people killed per year. This is a conservative estimate including only recorded deaths: the real total may be much higher.</li>\n<li>The annual economic cost of armed violence in non-conflict settings, in terms of lost <a href=\"/wiki/Productivity\" title=\"Productivity\">productivity</a> due to violent deaths, is <a href=\"/wiki/USD\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"USD\">USD</a> 95 billion and could reach as high as USD 163 billion - 0.14 percent of the annual <a href=\"/wiki/Global_GDP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Global GDP\">global</a> <a href=\"/wiki/GDP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"GDP\">GDP</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p>Armed violence reduction is therefore essential for the achievement of the <a href=\"/wiki/Millennium_Development_Goals\" title=\"Millennium Development Goals\">Millennium Development Goals</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Armed_violence_reduction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Small_Arms_Survey\" title=\"Small Arms Survey\">Small Arms Survey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Insecurity_Insight\" title=\"Insecurity Insight\">Insecurity Insight</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Armed_violence_reduction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Geneva Declaration key numbers: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.genevadeclaration.org/fileadmin/docs/Geneva-Declaration-Millennium-Development-Goals.pdf\">http://www.genevadeclaration.org/fileadmin/docs/Geneva-Declaration-Millennium-Development-Goals.pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\u0261</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Armed_violence_reduction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.genevadeclaration.org/home.html\">Geneva Declaration on Armed Violence and Development</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.un.org/millenniumgoals/\">Millennium Development Goals</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1269\nCached time: 20180903191136\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.036 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.042 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 113/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 356/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 88/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 791/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.004/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 525 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   24.960      1 Template:Reflist\n100.00%   24.960      1 -total\n  8.16%    2.037      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:30991666-0!canonical and timestamp 20180903191136 and revision id 787924357\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"Nonviolence"},{"sortkey":"","*":"War"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Conflict_(process)"}],"links":[{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Armed conflict"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Cr